### Improve the performance of TermsAggregation

When skywalking queries the topology map, it uses queryTopoInfo to query the corresponding information. When it finds that it takes a long time, the main time-consuming statements are as follows,add ` "execution_hint": "map",
         "collect_mode": "breadth_first",`there is about a 5-10x performance difference.

**My index table sw89_metrics-percent size is about 300GB/day**
```
POST /sw89_metrics-percent/_search
{
  "size": 0,
  "query": {
    "bool": {
      "must": [
        {
          "range": {
            "time_bucket": {
              "gte": 202204212336,
              "lte": 202204212351
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "terms": {
            "entity_id": [
              "xxx1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "term": {
            "metric_table": "service_sla"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "aggregations": {
    "entity_id": {
      "terms": {
        "field": "entity_id",
        "size": 1
      },
      "aggregations": {
        "percentage": {
          "avg": {
            "field": "percentage"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```
